---
// CommonProblems — Grid of real issues users search for, completely different from InstallGuides
---

<section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-carbon-950 via-carbon-900 to-carbon-950"></div>
  
  <div class="section-container relative z-10">
    <!-- Section header with left alignment -->
    <div class="mb-12 max-w-2xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-ember-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008Z"></path></svg>
        Soluciones Rápidas
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-cream-50 mb-3">
        ¿Tienes algún problema?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-cream-400 text-lg">
        Estos son los problemas más comunes que resolvemos a diario. Haz clic para ver la solución.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Problems grid — 3x2 -->
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      
      <!-- Problem 1 -->
      <a href="/faq#pantalla-negra" class="problem-card group">
        <div class="problem-icon bg-red-500/10 text-red-400">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 20.25h12m-7.5-3v3m3-3v3m-10.125-3h17.25c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V4.125c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H3.375c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v12c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125Z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-cream-100 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-colors">Pantalla negra al abrir</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-cream-500 mt-1">Solución: reiniciar caché de la app y verificar conexión</p>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-cream-600 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"></path></svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Problem 2 -->
      <a href="/faq#se-congela" class="problem-card group">
        <div class="problem-icon bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-cream-100 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-colors">Se congela en deportes</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-cream-500 mt-1">Cambia la fuente del canal o usa la opción "Auto" de calidad</p>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-cream-600 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"></path></svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Problem 3 -->
      <a href="/faq#error-autenticacion" class="problem-card group">
        <div class="problem-icon bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 5.25a3 3 0 0 1 3 3m3 0a6 6 0 0 1-7.029 5.912c-.563-.097-1.159.026-1.563.43L10.5 17.25H8.25v2.25H6v2.25H2.25v-2.818c0-.597.237-1.17.659-1.591l6.499-6.499c.404-.404.527-1 .43-1.563A6 6 0 1 1 21.75 8.25Z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-cream-100 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-colors">Error de autenticación</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-cream-500 mt-1">Verifica que tu suscripción esté activa y reinicia sesión</p>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-cream-600 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"></path></svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Problem 4 -->
      <a href="/faq#favoritos" class="problem-card group">
        <div class="problem-icon bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-400">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 0 1 1.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 0 0 .475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 0 0-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 0 1-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.562.562 0 0 0-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 0 1-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 0 0-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.562.562 0 0 1 .321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 0 0 .475-.345L11.48 3.5Z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-cream-100 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-colors">¿Cómo agrego canales favoritos?</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-cream-500 mt-1">Mantén presionado el canal → "Agregar a favoritos"</p>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-cream-600 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"></path></svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Problem 5 -->
      <a href="/faq#control-remoto" class="problem-card group">
        <div class="problem-icon bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5h3m-6.75 2.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H6.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 4.5 4.5v15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-cream-100 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-colors">No funciona el control remoto</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-cream-500 mt-1">Descarga la app de control remoto para celular como alternativa</p>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-cream-600 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"></path></svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Problem 6 -->
      <a href="/faq#sin-sonido" class="problem-card group">
        <div class="problem-icon bg-rose-500/10 text-rose-400">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 9.75 19.5 12m0 0 2.25 2.25M19.5 12l2.25-2.25M19.5 12l-2.25 2.25m-10.5-6 4.72-4.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.28.53v15.88a.75.75 0 0 1-1.28.53l-4.72-4.72H4.51c-.88 0-1.704-.507-1.938-1.354A9.009 9.009 0 0 1 2.25 12c0-.83.112-1.633.322-2.396C2.806 8.756 3.63 8.25 4.51 8.25H6.75Z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-cream-100 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-colors">Audio sin sonido</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-cream-500 mt-1">Cambia la pista de audio en ajustes del reproductor</p>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-cream-600 group-hover:text-ember-400 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"></path></svg>
      </a>

    </div>

    <!-- View all link -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <a href="/faq" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-ember-400 hover:text-ember-300 font-semibold transition-colors">
        Ver todas las preguntas frecuentes
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.06);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .problem-card:hover {
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6);
    border-color: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
  .problem-icon {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
</style>
